&lt;p&gt;Funny story, though, this particular documentary caught my sight about a year ago, yet I didn&amp;apos;t start until this girl I have a crush on talked about it the other day. I&amp;apos;ve always been keen at documentaries about nature and history, but this gives me another view at humanity social documentaries.&lt;/p&gt;
